This directory contains ASAP defects
====================================

Each defect gets a defect number assigned and a file is created in the
directory containing the traffic on the defect.

The bug number is solely determined by the last entry in this directory.

* Defects/bugs are sent to asap@atnf.csiro.au
* assign bug id  asap0000, asap0001 ...
* add bugs/asapNNNN.txt for new defect

* Bug fixes have to be cvs tagged with the bug id
* trunk has to be merged with the fixes branch


MM20050315
